{"tid":382372,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇TEDx Talks？","createTime":"2017-08-31T15:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T18:38:38.000Z","uid":96262,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"542ae3b07dfa7996648112f013d33207a935c0ae","tid":382372,"uid":96262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:52:17.000Z","msg":"自從睇過一個女仔既TED talk就開始成日睇，每一個講者既主題都好有趣，內容好新鮮好豐富，學下public speaking又好，學聽listening又好，冇野做又好，ted talk個十幾廿分鐘一定唔會浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我呢幾日又睇左幾集幾想同人分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. Why I stopped watching porn<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gRJ_QfP2mhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgRJ_QfP2mhU&d=aTI0xW5AaQCkVNzvabHkVE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5780b644\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gRJ_QfP2mhU</a><br />\n<br />\n2. I am not your Asian stereotype <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_pUtz75lNaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_pUtz75lNaw&d=aTI0xW5AaQCkVNzvabHkVE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2154e2ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_pUtz75lNaw</a><br />\n<br />\n3. My philosophy for a happy life<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/36m1o-tM05g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F36m1o-tM05g&d=aTI0xW5AaQCkVNzvabHkVE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a928a24c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/36m1o-tM05g</a><br />\nBtw, RIP Sam<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. Philosophy in prison<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cMXFiYhm79g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcMXFiYhm79g&d=aTI0xW5AaQCkVNzvabHkVE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0a9365ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cMXFiYhm79g</a><br />\n<br />\n最後呢一個女仔，亦都係我中四時候睇完覺得好impressive既一集<br />\n5. I'm 17<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0OkOQhXhsIE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0OkOQhXhsIE&d=aTI0xW5AaQCkVNzvabHkVE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=f5fe6ff1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0OkOQhXhsIE</a><br />\n<br />\n內容黎講其實唔係偏向professional 既，因為我睇太pro既野未必跟到，所以以上既都係輕鬆啦，年輕為主，大家有睇過咩印象深刻既ted talk不妨放低條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1d63c2743ae9f720a3a0dc25d094675481e2da","tid":382372,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"最記得有集講gay佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到gay佬係自然嘅產物，因為gay佬擅於化解人與人之間嘅紛爭，擅於凝聚家庭，人際關係較好，聰明d<br />\n相反異性戀就比較有攻擊性<br />\n<br />\n我心諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55cfa08c6aa4257e2af97e9f9cfd11dc7695486","tid":382372,"uid":60422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"記得mc jin都有講過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e9081800edeb8629e3eceda5a146159c65e863","tid":382372,"uid":41887,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"Tedx唔係阿豬阿狗都搞得既咩？"},{"pid":"c337244c8444e2388a9d0bd680500cc8532d6206","tid":382372,"uid":23560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:20:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=WptaDlwq8cI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWptaDlwq8cI&d=aTI0xW5AaQCkVNzvabHkVE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=66c10997\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=WptaDlwq8cI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf87d770f9c7f14e42b127a4ab3c0acdad96504d","tid":382372,"uid":75364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"好鍾意呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDepression, the secret we share<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ted.com/